			<DIV>
<DIV><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? 10pt; **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: FONT-FAMILY:><SPAN red? **Zowie**?COLOR:>There has been no further update at this time regarding any of the old issues on your class list.&nbsp; I have altered the list to reflect the new items added and submitted.</SPAN></DIV></SPAN></DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>1. Knight tanking is too far behind Warriors and too close to non tanking classes. <FONT color=#ff0000>(currently being evaluated)</FONT>
<P><SPAN>2. SK's are supposed to be tied as the 2nd best tank but have the lowest damage avoidence of all melee classes. <FONT color=#ff0000>(currently being evaluated)</FONT></SPAN></P>
<P><SPAN>3. SK spellbook needs to scale to evolving content better. <FONT color=#ff0000>(currently being evaluated)</FONT></SPAN></P>
<P><SPAN>4. It is currently too tough for us to channel spells. <FONT color=#ff0000>(currently being evaluated)</FONT></SPAN></P>
<P><SPAN>5. Deathpeace is no longer sufficent as an FD tool. <FONT color=#ff0000>(currently being evaluated)</FONT></SPAN></P>
<P><SPAN>6. Our spell based aggro needs fixed and designed to scale. <FONT color=#ff0000>(currently being evaluated)</FONT></SPAN></P>
<P><SPAN>7. Knight DPS while not meant to be the highest should be higher than Bards. Far more progressed SK's can be KS'ed by Bards with ease from sheer lack of DPS on our part. <FONT color=#ff0000>(currently being evaluated)</FONT></SPAN></P>
<P><SPAN>8. A method to reduce damage allowing us to compete with Paladin stuns <FONT color=#0000ff>(NEW)</FONT></SPAN></P>
<P><SPAN></SPAN><SPAN>9. An upgrade to Leech Touch, it provides less of a HP swing, cannot be focused, cannot be disced, costs more AA, and prevents us from using our other HT to use. <FONT color=#0000ff>(NEW)</FONT></SPAN></P>
<P><SPAN>10. Removal/Refund of SCS or a toggle added to it. <FONT color=#0000ff>(NEW)</FONT></SPAN></P>
<P><SPAN>Ky</SPAN></P></DIV>
