<BLOCKQUOTE>
<DIV>
<P class=MsoNormal **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0in TEXT-ALIGN: 0pt; justify?><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?>1. Knight tanking is too far behind Warriors and too close to non tanking classes. <FONT color=#ff0000>(currently being evaluated)<namespace prefix = o ns = "http://www.lithium.com/unique/URI"></FONT> </P>
